title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E24 Edge of Doom
description:
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea

S04E24
Edge of Doom

Airdate: March 17, 1968

- One of 26 episodes from Season Four which are not yet on DVD
- Remastered audio and video from VHS
- FULL-LENGTH EPISODE with scenes missing from SciFi Channel version
- Compatible with stand-alone DivX players!

Informed that one of the crew is an impostor, Nelson tries to break down the most probable suspect: Crane (David Hedison).

Nelson: Richard Basehart. Morton: Bob Dowdell. Kowalski: Del Monroe. Sharkey: Terry Becker. Patterson: Paul Trinka.
